{"tid":1223941,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[東南亞國家J出血] 「東京奧運會」動漫加入參賽國旗，輝煌條紋變武士","createTime":"2019-06-15T00:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T11:23:14.000Z","uid":75050,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c6bdcd3e5e31b99c7bf19eb9bd318741beefdf28","tid":1223941,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:23:56.000Z","msg":"<strong>「東京奧運會」動漫加入參賽國旗，輝煌條紋變武士</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FaEJt01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFaEJt01.jpg&h=3b733c1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本是一個動漫非常發達的國度。2020年東京奧運會的到來，網上時不時出現一些花邊消息，有些網友甚至希望奧運項目出現動漫角色。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://world-flags.org/?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fworld-flags.org%2F%3F&d=YB8lrFeyQ%2BkzHCEHpdql8OaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=2808e279\" target=\"_blank\">https://world-flags.org/?</a><br />\n<br />\n其中代表馬來西亞的動漫武士設計， 其頭戴黃色新月和芒星的帽子，身穿藍底以及紅白相間的武士裝。 這位動漫武士一身打扮，完全就是代表馬來西亞的輝煌條紋（#JalurGemilang）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NaFkwfk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNaFkwfk.jpg&h=163fcc3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在為各國國旗設計動漫角色之餘，同時也介紹有關國家的文化背景，不過，一切以日文為主。<br />\n<br />\n其他東南亞國家如新加坡、泰國、印尼、菲律賓、越南的國旗也分別加入動漫元素。 當然少不了體育強國如美國、中國、澳洲等，至於東道主日本也有。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>印度尼西亞</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EXpYhVz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEXpYhVz.jpg&h=1a7c5a2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>新加坡</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BkYRCVA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBkYRCVA.jpg&h=0ca1a02d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>泰國</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNE5Hnf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNE5Hnf.jpg&h=b28aef91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>菲律賓</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hj9NbfB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhj9NbfB.jpg&h=42fb4e30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9dcf6638a1eccb33a1d1073c1d7166ec3deef8b","tid":1223941,"uid":75050,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:25:22.000Z","msg":"最型一定係越南，個個都係武士佢就陰陽師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hG9dRh5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhG9dRh5.png&h=a9a37bd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eeef05462c72bd396385130cdd0ef059f69c4739","tid":1223941,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:28:41.000Z","msg":"好好j<br />\n但唔知點解諗起sheldon cooper"},{"pid":"2b03b34ad0f60af8f33c4345dec3de08312c2990","tid":1223941,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:37:19.000Z","msg":"香港呢？"},{"pid":"fd140c2691a97921fdf967cf12ea800719376fc2","tid":1223941,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:41:30.000Z","msg":"大英帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aef33c2b23f2894dc97430d2c7e3005ea865148","tid":1223941,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b03b34ad0f60af8f33c4345dec3de08312c2990","tid":1223941,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:37:19.000Z","msg":"香港呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:42:29.000Z","msg":"未有"},{"pid":"04ae4c246f059504f0acf34aa94c4d0f55e03683","tid":1223941,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeef05462c72bd396385130cdd0ef059f69c4739","tid":1223941,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:28:41.000Z","msg":"好好j<br />\n但唔知點解諗起sheldon cooper"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:42:59.000Z","msg":"fun with flags"},{"pid":"aba361e35633b7a3b887dd1faada3cbf5ff2ae33","tid":1223941,"